* Single platform installation

./configure
make
make install

* Multi platform installation

mkdir linux
cd linux
../configure
make
make install

* bootstraping (lib)

make bootstrap

* configuration parameters

--prefix=<dir>: default is /usr/local/oz

* required variables default to /usr/local/{include,lib}

$oz_tk_lib_dir
$oz_tk_inc_dir
$oz_x11_lib_dir
$oz_x11_inc_dir
$oz_gmp_lib_dir
$oz_gmp_inc_dir

* TIPS:

./configure --no-recursion # create Makefile only in current directory
